💡 Placement Tip

In placement aptitude tests, Harmonic Progression is usually tested through basic concepts rather than lengthy calculations. The key idea is simple: convert the HP into an AP by taking reciprocals, then solve the problem using AP formulas and properties. If you remember that AP → Difference, GP → Ratio, HP → Reciprocals form an AP, you can solve most HP questions in 30–60 seconds.
